Rare pictures of Haitham Ahmed Zaki with his father Ahmed Zaki and his mother Hala Fouad .. See
07 Nov 2019, 11:15 by Aya Atef
The death of the artist Haitham Ahmed Zaki shocked the artistic community and the public, due to his sudden death at an early age, where he did not exceed the age of 35 years, after suffering a sudden drop in blood circulation. Haytham Ahmed Zaki died at the same age of death of his mother, 35, the age of death that brought the son together. His mother, the retired artist Hala Fouad, who married Ahmed Zaki and gave birth to their son Haitham before they separated later. In the early hours of Thursday morning, the young artist Haytham Ahmed Zaki died at the age of 35 years;
